{"tid":2403824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警拘一中年女子 涉紅磡區內多處塗寫「721」、「831」等字句","createTime":"2021-02-11T10:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T16:41:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f752beddd070de4732390e0fa22b5bb1a61c92fe","tid":2403824,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5191&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=27049284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5191</a><br />\n<br />\n【資訊部整合】警方記者會表示，本月初接獲報案指紅磡區內有多處寫上「721」、「831」等字句。今天（11日）便衣警員於馬頭圍道巡邏時，發現一名57歲女子用筆塗污8處地方，包括垃圾筒、燈柱等。警員上前截查，並在女子身上搜獲4枝筆，懷疑與案有關，警方其後以涉嫌「刑事毀壞」罪名拘捕該名女子。警員亦於馬頭圍道一帶發現多20處懷疑與案有關的塗污，而被捕女子仍然在扣留調查中。<br />\n <br />\n消息來源：警方記者會（1730 11/2）<br />\n＊報道立場並不代表被捕組及資訊部立場"},{"pid":"c581e90d38c07d591fe32a08832d8762dc281696","tid":2403824,"uid":4574,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"刑事毀壞? <br />\n曾灶財又係?"},{"pid":"2374b6d43d2c19f75af537d9b911ce80a73b55e1","tid":2403824,"uid":76804,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:14:47.000Z","msg":"就黎同64一樣變禁數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c7e352d5ad25e049da412843847dd77cc7c6d9","tid":2403824,"uid":160592,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"何俊堯果單呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b345d1c1390b2d052cc42d7943c0eaf92592a1","tid":2403824,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal